http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/kerala/DIET-prepares-digital-study-materials/article13978238.ece

: Providing support to parents and their wards who aspire to excel in their academic pursuits, the District Institute of Education and Training (DIET) here, in association with IT@school, has come out with exhaustive digital study materials to make the learning process more interesting. The smartly programmed package — e-resource system for teachers (TERMS) contains resource materials in Malayalam and Kannada, that include 126 subject blogs prepared by 31 academic groups, 754 lessons, 5,000 resource materials to help class I to X students and their parents and teachers.It has resource materials, including video, audio, PowerPoint presentations. — Staff Reporter